dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Leon, sheet 13. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 43.0000. South Decimal Degree 42.0000. East Decimal Degree -5.0000. West Decimal Degree -6.0000. Alternate title: Leon, Spain. Polyconic projection. With Spanish-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Spain, 1:50,000, Instituto Geografico, 1921-43; Iberian Peninsula, 1:250,000, Geographical Section, General Staff, 1941, sheets S 3672-3680; Road Map of Spain and Portugal, 1:400,000, A.M.S., sheets 41-44, Third Edition, 1943; Railways of Spain and Portugal 1:1,500,000, G.S.G.S., 1941, corrected from intelligence Reports, 1942-44.".
